Class SequenceGlider<T extends IGlider>

java.lang.Object
com.github.yellowstonegames.smooth.SequenceGlider<T>
Type Parameters:
T - an IGlider type
All Implemented Interfaces:
IGlider
Direct Known Subclasses:
VectorSequenceGlider
@Beta public class SequenceGlider<T extends IGlider> extends Object implements IGlider
Runs more than one Glider in a sequence. Meant to be subclassed with a specific Glider type for T.
